text: Layyah is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Layyah may also refer to: == Places == *Layyah District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan) *Layyah Tehsil, a tehsil of district Layyah *Layyah, Sharjah, a village in the United Arab Emirates ==People== *Layyah Barakat, a Syrian-born writer. *Laylah Ali, an American visual artist. ==See also== * Laya (disambiguation) * *
